challengeName: CSFV Forums UI Prototype Update Part 3
detailedRequirements:
Task Overview

The goal of this challenge is to update the provided UI prototype as outlined below.

Task Requirements

  • We referencing production css and js files, the path changed, you need to remove the /min from all pages for css/js links.
  • In forums-advanced-search.html page, we want to have nested items in the category pick list, with ability to select parent or nested items from list. The change should also increase the width of the drop down list so the nested items text can fully appear.
  • The changes should be applied to the 6 prototypes in the attached UI Prototype zip file in challenge forums.

Deliverables

The updated UI prototypes with updated readme html file about changes.
